      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for this diamond in the rough! While this vehicle has seen better days and will require some dedicated mechanical attention and TLC, it remains a fantastic project for a DIY enthusiast. It's an affordable entry point for someone looking to restore a car with great bones and plenty of stories to tell!",
