    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is currently not roadworthy. It requires a complete engine overhaul due to a seized block and has significant frame rust that needs professional attention. The interior is heavily worn with several missing components, and the electrical system is currently non-functional. This is strictly a project car or a parts donor for someone with the necessary tools and expertise.",
